<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1185.107005.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Tricholathys xizangensis sp. nov. A, B holotype male C, D paratype female A left male palp, ventral view B same, retrolateral view C Epigyne, ventral view D same, dorsal view. Abbreviations: AA = anterior arm of conductor; CD = copulatory duct; CO = copulatory opening; DP = digitiform process; Em = embolus; FD = fertilization duct; PA posterior arm of conductor; RTA = retrolaterial tibial apophysis; Sp spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/944664" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1185.107005.figure15>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Tricholathys xizangensis sp. nov. A, C-E holotype male B, F, G paratype female A male habitus, dorsal view B Female habitus, dorsal view C left male palp, prolateral view D same, ventral view E same, retrolateral view F epigyne, ventral view G same, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/944665" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

